    <item>
      <title>黄金连续第四天上涨，关注美国就业数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/gold-steady-after-three-day-gain-gain-with-us-payrolls-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商等待美国就业数据的公布，黄金价格连续第四天上涨，这将有助于决定美联储今年的政策前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/gold-steady-after-three-day-gain-gain-with-us-payrolls-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
