      <title>英国债券纠纷可能导致英国央行降息计划失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/bond-turmoil-raises-prospect-of-slower-bank-of-england-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，英国的市场动荡使人们关注点集中在工党政府身上，但经济学家表示，英国央行也必须减缓降息步伐，以应对这一挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/bond-turmoil-raises-prospect-of-slower-bank-of-england-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰冻天气挤压电力市场，英国风力发电量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-power-market-set-to-remain-tight-on-cold-windless-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气温骤降导致价格上涨，英国电力市场预计将于本周六迎来两周以来的最低风电发电量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-power-market-set-to-remain-tight-on-cold-windless-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:10:54 GMT</pubDate>
